A '''chilab''' was a [[Yuuzhan Vong]] "neural grub." It was inserted through the [[Sinuses|sinus cavity]] into one's brain, where it would interface with the optic nerve and record everything the subject saw through a period of time. [[Nom Anor]] used one to spy on the [[Bilbringi Shipyards]].

